	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002349_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p><placeName>Burnbank Road</placeName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><placeName><settlement type="town">Hamilton</settlement></placeName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="6" unit="chars"/>24 June 1865</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Napier</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>I thank you 
<lb/>very much for kindly 
<lb/>remembering me 
<lb/>in the Launch and 
<lb/>Trial Trip - <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I shall 
<lb/>be unable to avail 
<lb/>myself the pleasure 
<lb/>of seeing the launch 
<lb/>but I should like</p> 
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><!-- TODO SM: Is this an addSpan? If so, it needs to be coded as such. written along left hand side of first page - MH -->mention only to friends who can 
<w>appre-<lb break="no"/>-ciate</w> them <space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I am your 
<lb/><space extent="6" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002349_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">so very much to see
<lb/>an ironclad <w>per-
<lb break="no"/>forming</w> under
<lb/>your superintendance
<lb/>that if possible
<lb/>I shall be present
<lb/>as the trip tip of
<lb/>"<persName>Osman Ghazy</persName> <choice><sic>- "</sic><corr>" -</corr></choice>
<lb/>on Wednesday</p>
<lb/><p>In giving the
<lb/>usual intimation
<lb/>to my friends
<lb/><lb/>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002349_0003"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>I quite forgot to <add place="above" hand="#U" rend="gray small">768</add>
<lb/>send one to you
<lb/>and <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Napier</persName>
<lb/>about the death
<lb/>of my mother
<lb/>aged 82 - She
<lb/>said to me when
<lb/>going away seven
<lb/>years ago that
<lb/>she would like
<lb/>to have one of her
<lb/>"ladies" to lay her
<lb/>head in the grave
<lb/>that wish was granted
<lb/>for I performed

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002349_0004"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/>the last duty<reg>.</reg> to her yesterday 
<lb/>Tell <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Napier</persName> that the 
<lb/>great change appeared only 
<lb/>an hour before the dose 
<lb/>in quicker breathing - My 
<lb/><persName>sister</persName> said - "I think the 
<lb/>Saviour has come 
<lb/>for your mother - You 
<lb/>can lippen yourself to 
<lb/>him" - "Oh yes she said 
<lb/>in a way that only we 
<lb/><app><rdg><term type="nationality">Scotch</term></rdg><rdg><term type="people">Scotch</term></rdg></app> can understand 
<lb/>gave a last look to our 
<lb/>little girl &amp; send "bonnie 
<lb/>wee lassie" closed her 
<lb/>eyes &amp; soon all was 
<lb/>still - We are thankful 
<lb/>to believe that she is safe 
<lb/>in the haven of mercy 
<lb/>These little things we </p>
			
